<div id="review_1735822121" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1735822121" />
    <a title="Sean Blake" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/25471005-sean-blake"><img alt="Sean Blake" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1528978476p2/25471005.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1735822121?book_show_action=true">Aug 22, 2016</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Sean Blake" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Sean Blake" href="/user/show/25471005-sean-blake">Sean Blake</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9781847679369" href="/book/show/12070697-pereira-maintains">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/25471005-sean-blake?shelf=fiction">fiction</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1735822121" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14862568551094098822"><i>Pereira Maintains</i> is a surprisingly wonderful short novel. Written in a deceptively simple style, writer Antonio Tabucchi manages to successfully combine Catholic guilt, spirituality, philosophy, politics, Portugese history, love, memory and death in a quirky, sometimes humourous and classically European novel.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


